<h2 id="about-me">About Me</h2>

<p>I am currently a master’s student studying Complex Adaptive Systems under the Department of Applied Physics at the Chalmers University of Technology. Before I went into the realm of Complexity Science I had finished my bachelor’s study in Forestry Science. My topics of interest including but not limited to Ecology, Swarm Intelligence, Interdisciplinary Science.</p>

